  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will evaluate the effect of preoperative education on postoperative opioid.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators propose a randomized trial to be performed at the Cleveland Clinic.&#xD;
      Patients will be assigned to: 1) an educational video focused on postoperative analgesia&#xD;
      modalities, opioids, and realistic pain expectations (analgesic education); or, 2) an&#xD;
      educational video focused on other aspects of the perioperative experience.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
